Section 9: Developing Web Applications
 Lecture 9.1 Understand web applications in the microservices world

* Web Applications and Microservices
  * We're back to client-server era architecture
  * Often with many different clients
    * iOS/Android/Windows, Phone/Tablet/Desktop
  * Web applications are just another client
    * Single Page Applications (SPA)
    * Service Oriented Front End Architecture (SOFFA)
 
* What is SOFFEA ?

  Client                                                       Server
  Application (html, css, js)    <----- Downloads----        Web Server
                                 ------ Calls -------        REST API